  -i issuer-cert  required  path or url of issuer x509 cert
  <span class=3D"_">-s</span> signed-cert  required  path or url of signed =
x509 cert
  -v              optional  verbose logging

  *WARNING*
  This script was made <span class=3D"keyword">for</span> educational purpo=
ses.
  VERIFICATION MAY BE WRONG, USE AT YOUR OWN RISK!
</code></pre>

